      <title>欧洲对美联储大幅降息持谨慎态度</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/europe-shows-wariness-to-jump-onto-fed-s-big-cut-bandwagon</link>
      <description><![CDATA[从伦敦到法兰克福的政策制定者都表示，他们无意跟随美国迅速削减借贷成本，这在全球宽松速度问题上引发了跨大西洋联盟的新分歧。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/europe-shows-wariness-to-jump-onto-fed-s-big-cut-bandwagon</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:43:25 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>欧盟 Illumina 败诉 荷兰呼吁获得更多交易权力</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/eu-s-illumina-defeat-sparks-dutch-call-for-more-deal-powers</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在欧盟对更多小型交易进行审查的尝试遭到欧盟最高法院的否决后，荷兰竞争监管机构正在寻求加强权力，以调查这些可能破坏新兴科技市场竞争的交易。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/eu-s-illumina-defeat-sparks-dutch-call-for-more-deal-powers</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:33:37 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>Steward Health 首席执行官因藐视法庭罪遭参议院委员会判刑</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/steward-health-ceo-held-in-criminal-contempt-by-senate-committee</link>
      <description><![CDATA[负责调查 Steward Health Care 倒闭案的美国参议员周四投票通过了针对这家陷入困境的医疗系统的首席执行官的民事和刑事藐视法庭决议，因为他拒绝接受传票，拒绝就其在公司资金管理不善中所扮演的角色出庭作证。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/steward-health-ceo-held-in-criminal-contempt-by-senate-committee</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:18:16 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>印度禁止 Axis Bank 子公司管理新债发行</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-bars-axis-bank-unit-from-managing-new-debt-offerings</link>
      <description><![CDATA[印度资本市场监管机构禁止 Axis Capital Ltd. 担任印度公司新债发行的管理人，这是该国证券市场的最新一次打击行动。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/india-bars-axis-bank-unit-from-managing-new-debt-offerings</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 15:05:58 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>耶伦称美联储降息是“积极信号”，政策仍具限制性</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/yellen-says-fed-cut-positive-sign-policy-still-restrictive</link>
      <description><![CDATA[财政部长珍妮特耶伦表示，美联储周三的降息“对美国经济来说是一个非常积极的信号”，反映了降低通胀方面取得的进展和保护就业市场的决心。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/yellen-says-fed-cut-positive-sign-policy-still-restrictive</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 14:54:33 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>埃及将红海地区作为旅游热点</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/egypt-earmarks-red-sea-spots-in-search-of-more-tourism-megadeals</link>
      <description><![CDATA[埃及政府表示，已划出红海沿岸的五个区域供投资者开发旅游业，希望能够效仿今年早些时候在地中海达成的一项大型交易，帮助该国克服严重的经济危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/egypt-earmarks-red-sea-spots-in-search-of-more-tourism-megadeals</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 14:24:50 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>普利兹克表示芝加哥应考虑解决预算危机的所有措施</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/chicago-should-mull-all-fixes-for-budget-crisis-pritzker-says</link>
      <description><![CDATA[伊利诺伊州州长 JB Pritzker 周三表示，由于芝加哥明年面临近 10 亿美元的赤字，该市需要尽一切可能解决预算危机。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/chicago-should-mull-all-fixes-for-budget-crisis-pritzker-says</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 14:13:32 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>以色列加强战争讨论 爆炸设备死亡人数上升</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/exploding-gadgets-deathtoll-rises-in-lebanon-as-israel-steps-up-war-talk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[据当地政府称，本周黎巴嫩发生的一系列对讲机和传呼机爆炸事件造成的死亡人数已上升至 37 人，这表明疑似以色列针对真主党武装分子的一系列袭击造成了多么严重的破坏。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/exploding-gadgets-deathtoll-rises-in-lebanon-as-israel-steps-up-war-talk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 12:02:11 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>选举临近，突尼斯监禁总统两名竞争对手之一</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/tunisia-jails-one-of-president-s-two-opponents-weeks-before-vote</link>
      <description><![CDATA[突尼斯总统凯斯·赛义德在 10 月份选举中的两名对手之一被判处 20 个月监禁，其竞选团队表示，此举是为了在已因大规模逮捕批评者而受到影响的选举中排挤挑战者。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/tunisia-jails-one-of-president-s-two-opponents-weeks-before-vote</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 07:56:51 GMT</pubDate>
    </item>
    <item>
      <title>美国议员拒绝游说 中资科技公司面临风险</title>
      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/china-s-failing-us-lobby-playbook-puts-tech-companies-at-risk</link>
      <description><![CDATA[美国议员向中国发出信号，无论11月大选后谁控制华盛顿，世界第二大经济体及其企业在可预见的未来都将在美国面临严峻挑战。]]></description>
      <guid>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2024-09-19/china-s-failing-us-lobby-playbook-puts-tech-companies-at-risk</guid>
      <pubDate>Thu, 19 Sep 2024 00:00:00 GMT</pubDate>
